{"tid":2070406,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警長截查少年遭阻擋　清潔工阻差辦公罪成判社會服務令","createTime":"2020-06-19T06:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T06:14:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47ecbc2dd8033a4d0eab981a73615a75cfb9f38f","tid":2070406,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:13:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532951-20200619.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532951-20200619.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C85RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=66e0c305\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532951-20200619.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cd785c43\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532951-20200619.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n去年8月深水埗警署附近有示威者聚集，一名警長要求一名少年出示身份證時，遭一名清潔工人阻擋，最終少年逃去。清潔工人受審後被裁定阻差辦公罪罪成，於九龍城裁判法院被判160小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n辯方表示，感化官形容被告合作，建議判81至160小時社會服務令，加上被告已被還押超過10天，工作「手停口停」，希望法庭給予機會。裁判官黃國輝表示，被告最後一次案底已是2014年，從未干犯同類罪行，雖然控罪嚴重可判囚，但強調判社會服務令等同監禁，刑罰非輕。<br />\n<br />\n50歲男被告何永隆被控於去年8月5日於深水埗欽州街與長沙灣道交界，阻礙獲合法授權執行公務的公職人員。"},{"pid":"82720264de76179857c24d8f5dec3eeca0ff2b4d","tid":2070406,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:14:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【讓社工家棟看見我們的支持】眾籌登報聯署</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2070370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2070370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyziMpX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyziMpX.jpg&h=1fbdbdaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CuE3c4Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCuE3c4Y.jpg&h=d59182d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B6UiMpY.jpg\" data